                    yaṃ kāraṃ mārutākhyaṃ ∙ ram iti hutabhujaṃ vaṃ jalaṃ maṇḍalaṃ tat ∙<lb/>
                    [1v2] laṃ kāraṃ bhūmisaṃjñaṃ ∙ tadupari mam idaṃ merusaṃjñaṃ tadurdhvaṃ ||<lb/>
                    [1v3] prajñopāyātmakaṃ kṣaṃ ∙ ham iti gaganataḥ śūnyanairaṃjanīyaṃ ∙<lb/>
                    [1v4] kūṭaṃ saptākṣarīyaṃ ∙ praṇamata satataṃ ∙ vajrapātādyahārīṃ || 1 ||
                </p>
